file.name: api.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 0.1.0
  title: Test

components:
  schemas:
    Random:
      type: object
      required:
        - list
      properties:
        list:
          allOf:
            - $ref: "#/components/schemas/Collection"
    Collection:
      items:
        $ref: '#/components/schemas/Item'
      type: array
    Item:
      required:
        - first
      properties:
        first:
          type: string
